{"tid":1708223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動Post]  1112 二 罷 ·繼 續 塞","createTime":"2019-11-11T13:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T01:51:10.000Z","uid":201146,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2c6da84528ef9cf29a25fb38a5b87561ec6ae8a4","tid":1708223,"uid":201146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/vxBpTKS.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1112．周圍塞<br />\n0600公佈集合地點<br />\n0630集合及分工<br />\n0700開始做嘢<br />\n<br />\n頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielam&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=468bbc82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam</a><br />\n車隊: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DVetIahwzUxmGuSCDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLC07DVetIahwzUxmGuSCDg&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=713290b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DVetIahwzUxmGuSCDg</a><br />\n05:00號角手: <a href=\"http://t.me/SoundTheBugle1111am\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSoundTheBugle1111am&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=acc508d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/SoundTheBugle1111am</a><br />\n-<br />\nRB攻略：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/engineernoextradition/908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fengineernoextradition%2F908&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=633f131c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/engineernoextradition/908</a><br />\n火魔法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/engineernoextradition/873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fengineernoextradition%2F873&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=680abbb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/engineernoextradition/873</a><br />\n爆炸魔法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/engineernoextradition/915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fengineernoextradition%2F915&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=9942fe6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/engineernoextradition/915</a><br />\n<br />\n其他魔法睇 @engineernoextradition pinned message<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日戰績</span></span><br />\n【0930】港鐵服務受阻，詳情如下：<br />\n觀塘線：黃埔站關閉<br />\n荃灣線：葵芳站關閉<br />\n將軍澳線：將軍澳站至北角站服務暫停<br />\n東涌線：東涌站至欣澳站服務暫停<br />\n西鐵線：元朗站至屯門站服務暫停<br />\n東鐵線：火炭站至羅湖站服務暫停<br />\n馬鞍山線：石門站來往烏溪沙站服務暫停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟居於東鐵沿線，今朝同手足早起打爆黨鐵，<br />\n未夠8點就可以無代價地申請罷工，全日抗爭到依家。<br />\n<br />\n被企圖槍殺嘅同學依然危殆，我地訴求依然未被理會，<br />\n懇請手足聽日繼續努力塞爆香港交通，<br />\n行過掉少少野出街已經好夠！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"294d42178c0e821933c4712ae59cce78a9ed8a50","tid":1708223,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:47:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielam&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=468bbc82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam</a><br />\n1112黎明行動2.0"},{"pid":"a9f8f5dab75e2cce448fdc55288d74bb9b2f626e","tid":1708223,"uid":201146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"全民早起，繼續三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！"},{"pid":"52353b43570ddb8641a80cf8a81a9f546fe40579","tid":1708223,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"roadblock 要升級，要夠大唔易清啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCOr7Eo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCOr7Eo.jpg&h=e467864d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>朝早係春袋，阻人返工點得架？！<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n全民早起，繼續三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fcfcf7aec54d4915e854a18a88c2b901214303a9","tid":1708223,"uid":201146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:56:17.000Z","msg":"全民早起，繼續三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！"},{"pid":"5e5ccd6e88dca09bcead8c90748905f868ac1465","tid":1708223,"uid":47834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"Completely withdraw extradition bill <br />\n- Holistic withdrawal of unjust charges<br />\n- Independent commission of inquiry <br />\n- No riot labelling<br />\n- Authentic universal suffrage<br />\n<br />\nMake C.H.I.N.A. a censored word.<br />\n<br />\n1112三罷 <br />\n香港人報仇"},{"pid":"b9350159f32f67138b31b4fa27968982c41f0945","tid":1708223,"uid":47834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"Completely withdraw extradition bill <br />\n- Holistic withdrawal of unjust charges<br />\n- Independent commission of inquiry <br />\n- No riot labelling<br />\n- Authentic universal suffrage<br />\n<br />\nMake C.H.I.N.A. a censored word.<br />\n<br />\n1112三罷 <br />\n香港人報仇"},{"pid":"5b44dc5d4adbc8fcc898d131cc2567ca7dcf1edf","tid":1708223,"uid":201146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:58:21.000Z","msg":"孫子兵法話︰「圍城必闕」，即係包圍敵人時必定要留返一條路比佢走。<br />\n點解？<br />\n因為唔好逼到對方得返一個選擇，要俾對方有兩個選擇，所以佢必定會選擇較易嘅一個。<br />\n<br />\n塞死晒全部線<br />\n選擇︰<br />\n1. 落車清RB<br />\n結論︰只有一個選擇。今日可見有好多藍屍係會落車清RB，所以好快就通返車<br />\n<br />\n塞淨一條線<br />\n選擇︰<br />\n1. 落車清RB<br />\n2. 用淨返嗰條線走<br />\n選擇2，司機只需要小心避開RB，已經可以離開<br />\n選擇1，司機要落車慢慢拆野，先可以離開<br />\n結論︰多數人都係懶，選擇2係比較輕鬆，所以都會選擇做2<br />\n<br />\n事實上好多路塞淨一條同塞晒全部效果差唔多，但留返一條線會俾多一個選擇人地，咁佢必然唔會咁傻落車慢慢清，藍屍係非常自私的。<br />\n<br />\n而街頭抗爭都係一樣。黑狗每次都係包圍手足三面，只留返一條路俾手足走，原因係就「圍城必闕」。因為四面包圍，手足就只得返一個選擇就係拼死突圍，而留返一條路，就有兩個選擇︰1. 逃走；2. 拼死突圍，所以多數人都會選擇較容易嘅一個，逃走。<br />\n<br />\n古人智慧，後人利用！"},{"pid":"8749a5e20e43b7eb79573807d286854040e730ee","tid":1708223,"uid":227275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃色meme圖</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708107</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/c2jrn51.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"3c00304bedec49b286d944dd46ef290680e94819","tid":1708223,"uid":59451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee60733b45b41340d46c42f55eb7ce13fc442bb","tid":1708223,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:01:08.000Z","msg":"「黎明行動」低風險新職業 - 搬屋師/升降師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1704038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1704038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c17a84e6b5c9fa0d1037d32a8588fcde3805dbe1","tid":1708223,"uid":47834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"Completely withdraw extradition bill <br />\n- Holistic withdrawal of unjust charges<br />\n- Independent commission of inquiry <br />\n- No riot labelling<br />\n- Authentic universal suffrage<br />\n<br />\nMake C.H.I.N.A. a censored word.<br />\n<br />\n1112三罷 <br />\n香港人報仇"},{"pid":"cd48efcb4fd4534fef313caff7888a37909fe17a","tid":1708223,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"一野隊爆巴士側鏡"},{"pid":"1c8b91fd7d7890a5e62007653d92f01ffba65314","tid":1708223,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c9c2c0ae7cfea7c9af153104bc2c7a288a66d3e","tid":1708223,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85b1b8993b380ac9260f65084b8e7e49002dabed","tid":1708223,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:13:54.000Z","